item.title: /about/
item.description: I graduated from Stanford with a B.S. in Computer Science in 2016, worked as a software engineer at the financial technology startup Addepar until late 2020. I’m now at Princeton pursuing a Master’s in Computer Science. Outside of work, I like to draw ✎, as this webpage’s subtitle suggests. The Instagram account I’ve linked to hasn’t been updated in a while, but hopefully that’s changed by the time you’re reading this.
